org.cytoscape.dyn.internal.vizmapper
Interface DynVizMap<T>

Type Parameters:
T -
All Known Implementing Classes:
DynVizMapImpl
public interface DynVizMap<T>

DynVizMap is the interface to represent the graphical dynamics in time of a CyNetworkView and is implemented by DynVizMapImpl. This implementation is to be preferred over custom static VizMap, since it is much faster and reliable.

Author:
Sabina Sara Pfister
